{"tid":1217973,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"CSL 6月尾完約","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:41:49.000Z","uid":11883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1281fbc71e85d67097aff9c2696296bc3b585b","tid":1217973,"uid":11883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":19,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"屋企人個CSL Plan 6月尾完約<br />\n用量唔多  Prefer CSL 續約唔轉Number<br />\n請出招"},{"pid":"4d49666f10802dfd32997d15b34b96b2ba3481ab","tid":1217973,"uid":226392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2281ce4dee7505935882e4e54a4b07c5147c0eff","tid":1217973,"uid":225880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d9d1ac12a004ce7ad902078ad112a4d38bb4a24","tid":1217973,"uid":173831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7deb5e7881b39a665ecd3b1bccd1169a87353608","tid":1217973,"uid":244951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6017511714c56db9e46fa712e752ca4969377db4","tid":1217973,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"2014雨革、612當日已經證明班警犬全部都係冇良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下為集眾人之力結合成嘅圖集，希望大家可以幫手廣傳：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2299277576830901&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ec51afbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901</a><br />\n<br />\n612嗰日一位16歲女學生嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議大家可以聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完之後我好嬲，亦都好想喊，香港今時今日嘅景況，除咗班高官之外，班蓄生警犬亦都有份一手一腳造成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員瞄準頭部射擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=347388e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=76e1b15f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=3020b9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=4bffe32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=5d2a51ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=0643f7d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n事後嚟張大合照慶功先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議告上聯合國！向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀"},{"pid":"3734388454f5b89d94dcf734ce345b94427f844c","tid":1217973,"uid":228984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d36eb9138d19ed1870bb1b2ab7586a23bf0e120","tid":1217973,"uid":135879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f56a734c8e6e21298abb0b58bb6acee0c9fbc80","tid":1217973,"uid":188376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e62575d47e0658a0848d5c9f08944b67e00cf9b","tid":1217973,"uid":236311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e7cf752a9bee3b143d019f6ed19b184b9837bd3","tid":1217973,"uid":148454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"148782d283b4158e1830cc7750b4ce8afe2313a8","tid":1217973,"uid":251666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6dcfa524c5330854fea7bcdefa5a4bf4c1f2a4c","tid":1217973,"uid":93645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f56e2fab482a97703854fac849ab3aea6de7e95","tid":1217973,"uid":221879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"887ebcf78eb27c4974663c34b69236ede03279b8","tid":1217973,"uid":252531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2291965883dac37bb138048c56d62f9c10c9e95